title: Alessandro Moreschi - The Last Castrato (1902)
description:
The only recording of a castrato, recorded in Rome in two sets of sessions,
the first on 3 & 5 April 1902 and the second on 11 April 1904

More information about Alessandro Moreschi can be found at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alessandro_Moreschi
